    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor Water Resistant Collapsible Bag is the super lightweight day pack that won&#039;t weigh down your on-the-go lifestyle. This day pack is ultra-lightweight and is constructed out of water-resistant 190T polyester. Comes with zipper closures to secure your belongings up and can hold up to 10Ibs. The bag when in use measures 17&quot; x 11&quot; x 5.5&quot;. Collapsing this bag into its inner pocket converts it into a compact size that measures 5&quot; x 5&quot;, making this day pack an excellent addition to any travel pack or emergency kit. The Water Resistant Collapsible Day Bag is great for travel, hiking, or just the daily commute!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Pocket Travel Collapsible Day Pack Lightweight Water Resistant</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor Water Resistant Collapsible Bag is the super lightweight day pack that won&#039;t weigh down your on-the-go lifestyle.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Ultra Lightweight Day Pack</li>\n    <li>Holds up to 10Ibs.</li>\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> Water Resistant Nylon</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Green, Orange, Red</li>\n    <li><strong>Backpack Dimensions:</strong> 17&quot; x 11&quot; 5.5&quot;</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/BG-BBP102GR_Backpack_Green_3.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor Water Resistant Collapsible Bag is the super lightweight day pack that won&#039;t weigh down your on-the-go lifestyle\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> WPDPR7-916</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 706569170122</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> One Size</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This day pack is ultra-lightweight and is constructed out of water-resistant 190T polyester. Comes with zipper closures to secure your belongings up and can hold up to 10Ibs. The bag when in use measures 17&quot; x 11&quot; x 5.5&quot;. Collapsing this bag into its inner pocket converts it into a compact size that measures 5&quot; x 5&quot;, making this day pack an excellent addition to any travel pack or emergency kit.</p>\n  <p>The Water Resistant Collapsible Day Bag is great for travel, hiking, or just the daily commute!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Outdoor Water Resistant Collapsible Bag is the super lightweight day pack that won't weigh down your on-the-go lifestyle. This day pack is ultra-lightweight and is constructed out of water-resistant 190T polyester. Comes with zipper closures to secure your belongings up and can hold up to 10Ibs. The bag when in use measures 17\" x 11\" x 5.5\". Collapsing this bag into its inner pocket converts it into a compact size that measures 5\" x 5\", making this day pack an excellent addition to any travel pack or emergency kit. The Water Resistant Collapsible Day Bag is great for travel, hiking, or just the daily commute!.",
